        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-navy">TYPES</span>&nbsp; What is the best type of shower for a Liverpool home?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>It depends on your water supply. Electric showers work on any system and are the most common choice in Liverpool. Thermostatic mixer showers are best for homes with good pressure or an unvented cylinder. Power showers boost low pressure but need a hot water cylinder. Digital showers give the best control and are ideal for larger properties. We advise on the right choice at the quote visit.</p></div></details>
