        <details class="pf-faq-item"><summary><span class="pf-faq-tag pf-tag-navy">TIME</span>&nbsp; How long does shower installation take?</summary><div class="pf-faq-body"><p>A like-for-like electric shower replacement takes 2 to 3 hours. A new thermostatic mixer shower installation takes 2 to 4 hours. A walk-in shower enclosure and tray takes 1 day. A full walk-in tiled shower area takes 2 to 3 days including waterproofing and tiling. We confirm the timeline at the quote stage.</p></div></details>
